Create a simple fake store only with useContext and useReducere React Hooks 
in this simple app you can Increase and Decrease product in existing list
when decrease count come to Zero, product will remove and use can delete product anytime you want with delete button 
there is 2 filters system, by price and size 
when you filter size, after filter by price size filter active
there is a bascket icon with badge and when click on it, show total price 
